snippet.title: ESSENTURES - Trailer - (POKEMON + ZELDA INSPIRED GAME)
snippet.description:
Site: https://www.essentures.com/
A new Monster Catching Game, inspired by Pokémon and The Legend of Zelda!

Over 250 creatures that can be used as allies or turned into weapons! Action mixed with turn RPG, customizable Game Skin and much more!

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/essentures.game/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/j746WUg4ne
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Essentures
Twitter: https://twitter.com/essentures
